Class NamespaceManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • web.controller.communication.opcua.NamespaceManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    WebCommunication, org.eclipse.milo.opcua.sdk.server.api.AttributeHistoryManager, org.eclipse.milo.opcua.sdk.server.api.AttributeManager, org.eclipse.milo.opcua.sdk.server.api.MethodServices, org.eclipse.milo.opcua.sdk.server.api.MonitoredItemManager, org.eclipse.milo.opcua.sdk.server.api.Namespace, org.eclipse.milo.opcua.sdk.server.api.NodeManager, org.eclipse.milo.opcua.sdk.server.api.ViewManager

    public class NamespaceManager
extends Object
implements org.eclipse.milo.opcua.sdk.server.api.Namespace, WebCommunication
    Change class from Milo example. This class forwards the read and write (update) operations from a client to the virtual representation framework. Afterwards the answer from the manager is converted to a opc ua answer.
